"" Window Movement
" decrease width
nnoremap <C-H> <C-W><
" increase width
nnoremap <C-L> <C-W>>
" decrease height
nnoremap <C-K> <C-W>-
" increase height
nnoremap <C-J> <C-W>+
" move window in normal
nnoremap <A-h> <C-w>h
nnoremap <A-j> <C-w>j
nnoremap <A-k> <C-w>k
nnoremap <A-l> <C-w>l
" create windows using H, J, K, L
nnoremap <A-H> <C-w>v
nnoremap <A-J> <C-w>s<C-w>k
nnoremap <A-K> <C-w>s
nnoremap <A-L> <C-w>v<C-w>h
